-- Carlyle's Rubenstein Says Turkey, Egypt Positive Investment Opportunities
-- B y   C a m i l l a   H a l l
-- 2010-10-26T12:11:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/carlyle-s-rubenstein-says-turkey-egypt-positive-investment-opportunities.html
David Rubenstein, co-founder and
managing director of Carlyle Group, said he sees Turkey and
Egypt as attractive investment opportunities.  Rubenstein, speaking at a news conference at the World
Economic Forum in Morocco today, said the Middle East has an
opportunity to rival China and India.  To contact the reporter on this story:
